DataList.LocalizeJP: 問題ない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: No problem.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ここでも任務があるのか？
DataList.LocalizeEN: We are taking missions here too?

DataList.LocalizeJP: っ！ちょっと！変なとこ触るな！
DataList.LocalizeEN: H-hey! Don't touch me there!.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちっ！覚えとけよ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Tsk. Don't think I'll forget about this!

DataList.LocalizeJP: くそっ！なんでこんなことに！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Agh! Why did it end up like this!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 規則違反者はどこだ！？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Where are the perpetrators!?

DataList.LocalizeJP: さて、準備運動でもするか。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Now then, shall we do some warm-up exercises?

DataList.LocalizeJP: まったく、鬱陶しいやつらだった。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Phew, they were an annoying bunch.

DataList.LocalizeJP: これでようやく、ゆっくり休憩ができる。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Now I can finally take a break.

DataList.LocalizeJP: よし、行くぞ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: All right, let's go.

DataList.LocalizeJP: よし！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Great!.

DataList.LocalizeJP: いったん隠れる。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'll hide for the time being.

DataList.LocalizeJP: なっ、なんだ！？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Wh-what was that!?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 無駄だ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's useless.

DataList.LocalizeJP: これより、夏合宿のトレーニングを開始する。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Summer camp training begins now.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 砂のお城みたいに、跡形もなく壊してやる！
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'll turn you to dust like a sandcastle!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 場所を移動する。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Changing location.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 狙撃ポイントへ移動する。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Moving to sniping position.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ありがとう。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thank you.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちっ…。ちょっと浮かれすぎたか…
DataList.LocalizeEN: Tsk. Maybe I got too carried away...

DataList.LocalizeJP: 逃がすか！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Don't think you can run!

DataList.LocalizeJP: くらえ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Take this!

DataList.LocalizeJP: よし、早く次の場所へ行こう。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Good. Quick, to the next location.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 言っても聞かないバカには、銃弾をくらわせるしかない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: A fool who doesn't listen what they're told leaves me no choice but to feed them lead.

DataList.LocalizeJP: まったく……海だからといって浮かれすぎだ。バカどもめ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Seriously... fools get too carried away at the beach.

DataList.LocalizeJP: そらっ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Take that!

DataList.LocalizeJP: まったく、せっかくの休憩時間が！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ah, come on! Just when I had some time off.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 少しくらいゆっくりさせてくれ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Can't you let a girl have a break?!

DataList.LocalizeJP: せっかくの非番の日なんだけどな…。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It had to be during my day off...

DataList.LocalizeJP: 逃がすか！
DataList.LocalizeEN: You aren't going anywhere!

DataList.LocalizeJP: どんな状況でも逃がしはしない！
DataList.LocalizeEN: You didn't think I'd let you go because of this place, right?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 違反者には罰を！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Punish the perpetrators!

DataList.LocalizeJP: これも夏の合宿の成果だな。
DataList.LocalizeEN: This is thanks to the summer training camp.

DataList.LocalizeJP: なるほど。確かに技術が身についてるみたいだ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I see. I guess I've gotten the hang of it.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 夏だから、海だからってトレーニングを怠るわけにはいかない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Just because it's summer at the beach doesn't mean I'll neglect training.

DataList.LocalizeJP: うん、確かに成長してる。……ちょっと！どこを見てるんだ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Yes. I can tell I've grown. ...Hey! Where are you looking?!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生のこと……頼りにしてるから。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm counting on you, Sensei.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今年の夏は付き合ってもらうよ？なっ！いや、その、トレーニングの話！
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'll need you by my side this summer. W-wait! I meant, for training!

DataList.LocalizeJP: もしかして、ずっと私の後をつけてきたのか？……えぇ、嘘だろ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Don't tell me you were following me all along?... Eeeh, no way...

DataList.LocalizeJP: まったく……本当に不思議な人だ。ヘンタイで、大人なのに情けなくて。でも……なんだか放っておけない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Seriously, you are one strange person. You're a pervert, you're pathetic for an adult. But... I guess I can't let you go.
